### imutils
## for python in virtualenvs
1. in pycharm select interpreter as virtualenvs
2. add (plus sign) imutils (this installs it directly under virtualenvs)

## for python not in virtualenvs
# install imutils for python3
sudo pip3 install imutils

# install imutils for python2.7
sudo pip install imutils

### pyserial
## for python in virtualenvs
1. in pycharm select interpreter as virtualenvs
2. add (plus sign) pyserial (this installs it directly under virtualenvs)

## for python not in virtualenvs
# install pip3
sudo apt-get install python3-pip

# install pyserial for python3
sudo pip3 install pyserial

# install pyserial for python2.7
sudo pip install pyserial

